Zhaojin Mining Allots 500 Million Yuan for Purchases, SCMP Says

-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 
2011-03-07T20:19:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-07/zhaojin-mining-allots-500-million-yuan-for-purchases-scmp-says.html
Zhaojin Mining Industry Co. has
alloted 500 million yuan ($76 million) of its 2011 capital
investment budget for the purchase of  gold mines , the South
China Morning Post said, citing Chairman Lu Dongshang.  The company plans to acquire mining rights for 20 metric
tons of gold resources in China with the money, and is in talks
for purchases abroad, the Hong Kong-based English-language
newspaper reported today.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  